      node {
        id
        status
        createdAt
        url
        staticUrl
      }
    }
  }
}
```

With variables: `{ input: { projectId: "project-id", serviceId: "service-id", environmentId: "environment-id" }, first: 10 }`

All three ID parameters appear required based on the documentation examples, though the schema definition itself isn't fully detailed in the provided content.

